gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 121, Magic 115
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Stephen Curry's 36 points, six assists, four steals and four 3PM, the Warriors defeat the Magic, 121-115. Jonathan Kuminga added 19 points, six rebounds and four assists in the victory, while Paolo Banchero (27 points, 12 rebounds, five assists) and Franz Wagner (25 points, six rebounds, three assists) combined for 52 points for the Magic in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 16-17 on the season, while the Magic fall to 19-14.
